config BR2_PACKAGE_LIBESMTP
	bool "libesmtp"
	select BR2_PACKAGE_OPENSSL
	help
		SMTP client which manages posting (or submission of) electronic mail
		via a preconfigured Mail Transport Agent (MTA). It may be used as part of
		a Mail User Agent (MUA) or other program that must be able to post
		electronic mail but where mail functionality is not that program's
		primary purpose.

		http://www.stafford.uklinux.net/libesmtp/index.html
